  "concentration": true,
  "description": "You try to create illusory terrors in others' minds. Each creature of your choice in a 30-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point within range makes a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a target takes 10d10 Psychic damage and has the &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false] condition for the duration. On a successful save, a target takes half as much damage only.\n\nA Frightened target makes a Wisdom saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a failed save, it takes [[/damage 5d10 type=psychic]] damage. On a successful save, the spell ends on that target.",
